#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:1
msgid "City Construction"
msgstr "城市建设"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ya know what this wilderness needs?  A city!  Nothing brings out the energy of a place like urban development.  You'll help me build my city, right?"
msgstr "你知道这片荒野真正需要什么吗？一座城市！没有什么能像城市建设一样激发这片土地的活力。你会帮我建造城市吧？"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "NO?!  Waddayamean no?  Well then what good are ya, anyway?"
msgstr "不？！什么意思，你居然说不？"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "That's the spirit!  Now the first thing we'll need is raw materials.  Lots of raw materials.  So go out there and get some stuff!"
msgstr "就是这种精神！我们首先需要原材料。大量原材料。快去收集一些吧！"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "We need lots of raw materials.  I know it's a lot to ask, but once my—I mean—our city is complete, you'll see that it was all worth it."
msgstr "我们需要大量原材料。我知道要求很多，但一旦我的——不，咱们的城市建成，你就会明白这一切都是值得的。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted that you have the raw materials."
msgstr "告诉泰德你已经收集好了原材料。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wow!  It's a miracle you can carry all that stuff.  Here, take your reward.  Now I'll let ya in on the next phase of my plan."
msgstr "哇哦！你竟然能搬动这么多东西，真是奇迹。拿上你的奖励吧。现在，我要告诉你我计划的下一阶段。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "The raw materials you brought me will go a long way to getting our city started, but there's lots more to do yet.  The city will need a mine.  You don't mind building a mine, do ya?"
msgstr "你带来的原材料已经能让城市建设起步了，但还有很多工作要做。城市还需要一个矿场，你不介意建造矿场吧？"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "Start the excavation wherever ya feel like it, and that's where the people in our city can dig for riches, and us too!"
msgstr "随便从哪儿开始挖掘吧，这样城市里的居民和我们都能开采宝藏！"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you're having trouble finding precious minerals, place some torches in the dark caves.  Any sort of light will make it easier to see all those goodies underground!"
msgstr "如果找矿有困难，可以在黑暗洞穴里点上火把。哪怕一点光，也能帮你发现地下的宝贝！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted that you have the precious minerals."
msgstr "告诉泰德你已经收集到珍贵矿物了。"

#. (itstool) path: removestep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:61
#, no-wrap
msgid "G-g-g-gold!  And gems!  When ya spelunk ya bring the funk, my friend.  Here's your cut of our profits.  Now comes the fun part of building our city."
msgstr "金子——还有宝石！朋友，你这趟洞穴探险可真是满载而归啊！这是你应得的奖励。现在，最有趣的部分来了——建造我们的城市！"

#. (itstool) path: collectstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "We've gathered the raw materials.  We've built a mine for our city.  But doesn't that mine look lonely?  It's time to build some cottages to keep our mine company.  There are special items that make a house feel like a home, and not just a big block of dirt bricks."
msgstr "我们已经收集好原材料，也为城市建造了矿井。但矿井看起来有点孤单吧？是时候建一些小屋，让矿井不再寂寞。有些特别的物品能让房屋更像家，而不仅仅是一堆泥砖。"

#. (itstool) path: collectstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "There's no place like home.  There's no place like—oh!  I didn't see ya there.  If ya need help crafting, check your Recipe Book to learn how to craft different items."
msgstr "没有地方比家更温暖。没有地方比家——哦！我没看到你。如果你需要制作帮助，可以翻看配方书学习制作各种物品。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:88
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:109
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:119
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted that you have the items to build a proper house."
msgstr "告诉泰德你已经收集到建造房屋的物品了。"

#. (itstool) path: collectstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "Those beds look more comfortable to sleep on than a chubby goat.  You are a person of many skills, my friend.  Did ya build a few houses?  You should definitely do that if ya get a chance."
msgstr "这些床看起来比趴在胖山羊身上舒服多了。朋友，你真是多才多艺。你建了几间房屋呀？有机会一定要多建几间。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thank you for all your help, my friend.  I can truly see the city of my dreams, and it's all because of you.  As you continue your adventures in this land, you should build more houses!  And bigger houses!  And expand our city."
msgstr "谢谢你的帮助，朋友。我终于能看到梦想中的城市，这一切都多亏了你。在这片土地上继续冒险时，你应该建更多房屋！更大的房屋！把我们的城市扩展起来。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/City%20Construction.xml:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "Check back in once in a while.  I may have more work for ya.  Oh yeah!  This note came for ya while you were gone.  It's from that old wizard.  He says he's ready for ya.  Good luck on your adventures."
msgstr "时不时回来看看，我可能还有更多工作给你。哦，对了！你离开时收到的这张便条，是那个老巫师寄来的。他说他已经准备好了。祝你冒险顺利！"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:1
msgid "Dragon Helmet"
msgstr "龙盔"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Oi!  Can ya believe that dastardly Dragon Dolt?  Ya gotta help me clobber him!"
msgstr "嘿！你能相信那个卑鄙的蠢货龙王吗？你得帮我狠狠教训他一顿！"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Dragon Lord’s cruelty tore my family asunder.  I’ll never forgive myself for helpin’ him get tough again.  Together I hope we can undo what we have done."
msgstr "龙主的残暴毁了我的家人。我永远无法原谅自己竟帮过他增强实力。希望我们能一起弥补曾经的过错。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "The whole world is countin’ on you, Dragon Rider.  Don’t give up!"
msgstr "全世界都指望着你呢，龙骑士。别放弃！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted you have crafted the Dragon Helmet."
msgstr "告诉泰德，你已经打造好了龙盔。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Now that’s what I call a helmet!  Maybe we stand a chance after all."
msgstr "这才叫头盔！也许我们还有机会赢呢。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "All our work will be for nothin’ if the Dragon Lord continues his reign of terror.  Think of our city!  Anyway, that gross goblin came by lookin’ for ya.  Even he’s ticked about the Dragon Lord."
msgstr "如果龙主继续他的恐怖统治，我们的努力都白费了。想想我们的城市！不管怎样，那个讨厌的哥布林找你了。连他都被龙主气得不行。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Dragon%20Helmet.xml:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "Speak to Mr. Goblin about the next piece of dragon gear."
msgstr "去找哥布林先生谈谈下一件龙防具。"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:1
msgid "Monster Troubles"
msgstr "怪物麻烦"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Oi!  You’re back.  And not a moment too soon.  This monster problem is gettin’ out of hand."
msgstr "嘿！你回来了，可正好及时。怪物问题已经失控了！"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ever since ya took care of the Ice Dragon, the yetis in the snow country have been runnin’ amok.  I guess the old blizzard-blastin’ reptile kept those hairy frog-lookin’ things in check.  Ya have to take out the yetis, Dragon Rider!"
msgstr "自从你解决了冰龙以后，雪国的亚蒂萨斯就开始到处作乱。我猜那只老冰暴巨龙原本把这些毛茸茸、像青蛙的家伙控制住了。龙骑士，你得去消灭这些雪人！"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:20
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The yetis in the snow country are downright abominable...\n"
"\n"
"What?\n"
"\n"
"Why are ya smilin’?"
msgstr ""
"那些雪人可真是名副其实的“可憎雪怪”……\n"
"\n"
"什么？\n"
"\n"
"你怎么在笑？"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted you have slain the yetis."
msgstr "告诉泰德，你干掉了亚蒂萨斯。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Good job, Dragon Rider."
msgstr "干得漂亮，龙骑士！"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "Goblins!  I knew our trouble wasn’t over.  Dragon Rider, we’re under attack!  Stop the goblin invasion, before our whole city is overrun."
msgstr "是哥布林！我就知道麻烦还没完。龙骑士，我们正遭受攻击！在我们的城市被占领前，赶紧阻止哥布林入侵！"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some say the goblins are descended from the dragons, due to their similar features.  The scaly skin is where the comparison ends.  Goblins are so hideous, and downright rude!"
msgstr "有人说哥布林是龙的后代，因为他们有些相似的特征。不过就止于有鳞皮。哥布林丑得要命，而且非常粗鲁！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted you have slain the goblin warriors."
msgstr "告诉泰德，你干掉了哥布林战士。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "I knew I could count on you to take care of those goblins, Dragon Rider.  But I’ll be gosh darned if I haven’t figured out the source of these recent monster attacks."
msgstr "我就知道你能处理好那些哥布林，龙骑士。不过，如果我没搞清这些怪物袭击的源头，我可真是心里没底啊。"

#. (itstool) path: step/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Have you seen that one goblin who’s been trollin’ the region?  He’s an ugly one.  I saw him stirrin’ up trouble with the monsters, and I reckon he’s behind the recent wave of monster attacks."
msgstr "你看到那个在这片地区捣乱的哥布林了吗？长得丑死了。我看到他在挑唆怪物，我猜他就是最近怪物袭击浪潮的幕后黑手。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "With all the troubles we’ve had lately, I can barely hear myself think."
msgstr "最近麻烦接连不断，我几乎都无法好好思考了。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Monster%20Troubles.xml:73
#, no-wrap
msgid "Speak to Mr. Goblin about the recent monster attacks."
msgstr "去找哥布林先生，了解最近怪物袭击的情况。"

#. (itstool) path: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml/quest@title
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:1
msgid "Sailing the Seas"
msgstr "海上航行"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "So ya wanna be a seafarer, eh?  Sure!  I can get ya a boat."
msgstr "想当海上水手吗？当然可以！我可以给你一条船。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The greatest civilizations in history took to the sea, and we shall be no different.\n"
"\n"
"Gather the necessary supplies, then assemble your mighty galleon!"
msgstr ""
"历史上最伟大的文明都征服过海洋，我们也不例外。\n"
"\n"
"收集必要的物资，然后组装你那艘强大的大帆船！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted you have crafted the boat."
msgstr "告诉泰德，你已经造好了船。"

#. (itstool) path: craftstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Bon voyage, Dragon Rider.  May ya always have smooth sailin’."
msgstr "一路顺风，龙骑士。愿你永远风平浪静。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "Now that ya got a boat, I’ve got another task for ya.  Out in the sea there’s been a whole bunch of sharks chompin’ on things, makin’ trouble.  Get out there and show ‘em what we’re made of."
msgstr "现在你有船了，我还有另一个任务给你。海上到处都是鲨鱼乱咬东西、制造麻烦。快出海去，让它们看看我们的厉害！"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing%20the%20Seas.xml:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Duhhhhh nuh!  Duhhhhh nuh!  Duh nuh duh nuh dananananananana!"
msgstr "咚呜呜！咚呜呜！咚呜咚呜 咚啦啦啦啦啦啦！"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:54
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted you have slain the sharks."
msgstr "告诉泰德，你已经解决了那些鲨鱼。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "Is that a shark tooth stickin’ outta your knuckle?  Holy chum, Dragon Rider.  You’re one tough fisherman."
msgstr "你指节上那是鲨鱼牙？老天爷啊！龙骑士，你简直是个狠角色的渔夫。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "They say the dreaded Tentaclon rules the deep – a mighty monster with more legs than you can count!  Take him out, so the sea critters will be free to swim in peace, once again."
msgstr "据说，深海由可怕的肯塔克隆统治——那是一头强大的怪物，腿多得你根本数不清！把它干掉，这样海里的生物才能再次自由地安宁游动。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are rumors, Dragon Rider, of one ocean dweller even mightier than Tentaclon, but I dare not speak her name.  I hope you never hear it."
msgstr "龙骑士，有传闻说，还有一个海中生物比肯塔克隆更可怕。我甚至不敢提她的名字——希望你永远不会听到。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "I’m glad to see ya returned in one piece.  Go wash the ink off your hands and then come talk to me.  I have a message from His Wizardliness."
msgstr "很高兴你安然无恙地回来。先把手上的墨洗掉，再来找我。我有一条来自伟大的魔法师大人的消息。"

#. (itstool) path: step/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Sailing the Seas.xml:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "While you were out tanglin’ with Tentaclon, the Wizard told me he’s \"ready for ya,\" whatever that means.  I’d head over there and see what’s up."
msgstr "你去应付肯塔克隆的时候，魔法师跟我说：“他已经等着你了”，虽然我也不太明白这是什么意思。你最好过去看看发生了什么。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/intro
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary Giant.xml:23
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary Giant.xml:44
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary Giant.xml:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Oi!  Well if it ain’t me old friend the Dragon Rider.  I’ve got a rotten dinosaur problem.  Will ya get out there and trounce that tyrannosaur, pretty please?"
msgstr "嘿！这不是我老朋友龙骑士嘛。外面有只讨人厌的暴龙在闹事。能不能帮我把那家伙收拾掉？拜托啦？"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/desc
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:24
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:45
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "Don’t let its scraggly little arms fool ya.  One chomp from those big jaws and you’ll be a piece of used chewin’ gum, Dragon Rider."
msgstr "不要被它那弯曲的小胳膊所欺骗。但凡你被它的大颚咬中一下，你会被嚼得像块嚼过的口香糖一样，龙骑士。"

#. (itstool) path: info/label
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:29
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:50
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:71
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tell Ted you have slain the TRex."
msgstr "告诉泰德，你杀了暴龙。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:25
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "That’s the Dragon Rider I know!  Tomorrow I’ll have more dinosaurs for you to squash.  Heck, I’d give my own leg to someone who could get rid of them all."
msgstr "这才是我所知的龙骑士！但明天肯定还会有更多暴龙。很好，谁要是能把它们全解决，我连自己的腿都愿意送出去。"

#. (itstool) path: killstep/finish
#: UnityGame/Assets/Quests/Viking/Scary%20Giant.xml:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "You’ve thinned the herd of T-Rexes in this land, ole pal.  I can’t give ya my own leg (I need it for stuff) but I will give ya this other leg I found."
msgstr "老朋友，你让这片土地上的暴龙减少了。我不能把自己的腿给你(我自己需要它们)，但我可以帮你另外一个忙。"

